title: A mild, creamy yogurt
review: It took 2 rounds of fermentation to get the yogurt to thicken. Very mild taste, thick and creamy.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2020
name: LynVanW
title: My best product buy so far this year.
review: I love, love, love this product! I am just really enjoying the experience of making my own yogurt. I'm on my third batch of homemade skyr. The flavor is phenomenal and the texture continues to improve with each batch. Plus, the online support and encouragement that you get from the seller is a welcome addition. I like that this seller has a Facebook group and is happy to answer any questions that you have as well as share in your triumphs.
